OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F363A1784274472
OL,3,CPrisoner arrested after escaping
OL,4,Cduring hospital transfer
OL,6,FAn escaped prisoner who absconded
OL,7,Fafter being transferred to hospital to
OL,8,Freceive medical treatment has been
OL,9,Farrested and is in custody.
OL,11,FMarwan Jumaa, a Sudanese national
OL,12,Fdeemed to be a risk to himself and
OL,13,Fothers, is serving an indefinite
OL,14,Fsecure hospital sentence for attacking
OL,15,Ftwo women.
OL,17,FThe 20-year-old escaped after being
OL,18,Ftransferred from his secure hospital
OL,19,Ffacility to North Manchester Hospital
OL,20,Ffor medical treatment on Tuesday, 14
OL,21,FJuly.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/6
