OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,364,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36302
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F363A1784274472
OL,3,CPrisoner arrested after escaping
OL,4,Cduring hospital transfer
OL,6,FPolice had issued an urgent appeal for
OL,7,Fany information or intelligence on his
OL,8,Fwhereabouts, but announced in the
OL,9,Fearly hours of Friday, 17 July, that
OL,10,Fhe had been arrested by a member of
OL,11,FLancashire Constabulary.
OL,13,FA Greater Manchester Police (GMP)
OL,14,Fstatement said: "Thank you to everyone
OL,15,Fwho shared and responded to our appeal
OL,16,Fearlier this evening to help locate
OL,17,Fwanted man Marwan Jumaa.
OL,26,@vD@QOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/6
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,364,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F363A1784274472
OL,3,CPrisoner arrested after escaping
OL,4,Cduring hospital transfer
OL,6,F"Following extensive enquiries, we can
OL,7,Fconfirm that Jumaa has been arrested
OL,8,Fby our colleagues at Lancashire
OL,9,FConstabulary. He is currently in their
OL,10,Fcustody."
OL,12,FDetective Superintendent Nicola
OL,13,FMcCulloch, of GMP's serious crime
OL,14,Fdivision, said: "This has been a fast-
OL,15,Fpaced investigation which has involved
OL,16,Fa significant number of officers and
OL,17,Fresources from Greater Manchester
OL,18,FPolice.
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@IO]vD@QOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/6
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,364,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36304
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F363A1784274472
OL,3,CPrisoner arrested after escaping
OL,4,Cduring hospital transfer
OL,6,F"An observant Lancashire Constabulary
OL,7,Fofficer recognised Jumaa and acted
OL,8,Fswiftly to arrest him. He will now be
OL,9,Freturned to a secure hospital facility.
OL,11,F"I would like to thank the public for
OL,12,Ftheir support following our appeal.
OL,13,FOur call handlers received a
OL,14,Fconsiderable amount of information
OL,15,Ffrom members of the public and that
OL,16,Fassistance has been invaluable in
OL,17,Fhelping us locate Jumaa.
OL,19,F"We are extremely grateful for the
OL,20,Fsupport shown throughout this
OL,21,Finvestigation."
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@AOU{D@AOU}D@OO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/6
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
