OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,364,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36305
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F363A1784274472
OL,3,CPrisoner arrested after escaping
OL,4,Cduring hospital transfer
OL,6,FA CCTV video, which showed Jumaa
OL,7,Fleaving the hospital unaccompanied in
OL,8,Fa light blue T-shirt, had earlier been
OL,9,Fcirculated by police.
OL,11,FCourt records show that in January
OL,12,Fthis year Jumaa pleaded guilty to
OL,13,Fthree offences at Woolwich Crown Court.
OL,15,FThe offences, all committed on 17 July
OL,16,F2025 in London, were assaulting an
OL,17,Femergency worker, a police officer,
OL,18,Fthe robbery of a woman and inflicting
OL,19,Fgrievous bodily harm on a second woman.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/6
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
