CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F363A1784274472
OL,3,CPrisoner arrested after escaping
OL,4,Cduring hospital transfer
OL,6,FJumaa had been held at HMP Belmarsh in
OL,7,FMarch and sentenced for the offences
OL,8,Fin April.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/6
